config.jfmuy.interface=Interface
config.jfmuy.interface.comment=Options relating to the User Interface.
config.jfmuy.interface.overlayEnabled=Item List Enabled
config.jfmuy.interface.overlayEnabled.comment=Show the list of items next to open guis.
